# tests/ folder

This folder contains **exactly two** integration test files. Do not add a third.

- `holder.test.ts` — GAINE test holder verification against MariaDB
- `waitlist.test.ts` — community waitlist persistence

Shared fixtures live in `tests/fixtures/`. When adding coverage, extend one of the two files above — never create new `*.test.ts` files here.

Run: `npm test`
